# .ops/ holds immutable operational audit artifacts. Their whole value is
# byte-fidelity to exactly what ran against prod, so disable EOL/encoding
# normalization: CRLF line endings and UTF-16 console captures must survive
# verbatim (core.autocrlf=input would otherwise rewrite CRLF -> LF on commit).
*.json  -text
*.txt   -text
# READMEs are ordinary docs, not captured artifacts.
README.md text
